item.title: Find You
item.description: Spending every minute of the night Thinking what we did and what we had Every second counts this time Going up at the speed of light Although I’m stuck Although I’m lost We fall in love with an open heart You saw every teardrop running down my face Chased the shadows until morning came Were ever you are, I will find you Shooting at the brightest stars tonight (And) Saying words that could mean so much Every time I close my eyes I´m going up at the speed of light Although it`s wrong Although it´s love?
